      "comment": "INVICTUS TOMMY (2) is a newcomer for the Neil Rawlings kennel. Drawn well and should get his chance. Profiles strongly for this and can make an immediate impact. WATCH AND SEE (8) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (31.21) at this track behind Lavender Lane in a Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Bold showing expected. ADHANA SNAPPY (1) racing well without winning, placing at her last four runs. Last start finished 3rd in a Maiden on February 26 over 530m at this track behind Gina Gulla beaten 2 lengths (31.06). Overdue and expected to feature again. ADHANA LESTER (6) is worth including again after a top-three finish at first outing.",
